rows.label: tlk45300054_04_msg0001
rows.name:
I can't believe it... How could
they make Superbia's Divine Beast
do something so reckless?

rows.label: tlk45300054_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Little cracks are starting to show
all over Alba Margen, and it's taking
everything I have to fix them all.

rows.label: tlk45300054_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Apparently they even picked
up some worrying readings at
the Geothermal Mining Plant.

rows.label: tlk45300054_04_msg0004
rows.name:
It looks like things may have calmed
down for now, but how much longer can
the Divine Beast really hold up?
